  <releases>
    <release version="128.0esr-bb4" date="2024-07-15">
      <description>
         <p>Betterbird 128 ESR is based on Thunderbird's current ESR version. Refer to Betterbird's release notes for details. Note that Thunderbird 128 and hence Betterbird 128 is shipping with a broken backend causing IMAP folder corruption under some circumstances. IT MUST NOT BE USED IN PRODUCTION!!</p>
      </description>
